WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.620
Ugh. She promised me she'd never leave me again.

2
00:00:07.620 --> 00:00:10.630
Look.

3
00:00:10.630 --> 00:00:13.619
I'm not the father.

4
00:00:13.619 --> 00:00:17.000
That's why she left.

5
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.250
Give this fake report to Max.

6
00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:23.399
We'll handle the rest for us.

7
00:00:23.399 --> 00:00:27.420
She's been lying to you all along.

8
00:00:27.420 --> 00:00:34.200
I'm the one who's faithful to you, Max.

9
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:35.200
Yes!

10
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.200
To the airport, please.

